  "time_ut": 1656662223,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc7 \u0b8a\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd : \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Railway workers on strike: People in great distress",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Railway unions say railway workers, including railway guards and locomotive drivers, have begun an immediate strike.",
        "Due to scarcity of fuel in the country, people rely on public transport to carry out their daily life.",
        "In this case, such sudden dismissal protests have affected the normal life of the people."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
